title: Gustave Caillebotte Paris Street; Rainy Day Tote
description:
Tote developed from Gustave Caillebotte Paris Street; Rainy Day, 1877, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

Step out in style with this tote celebrating an iconic painting of Parisian life in 1877.

  • Dimensions: 16.5 x 12 x 4 in. Strap drop 11in.
  • Materials: Polycanvas, microfiber lining.
  • Zippered closure, three  internal pockets.
